        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>圆形头像框剪裁代码</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        userProfileImage = view.findViewById(R.id.user_profile_image);</span><br><span class="line">button_user_nickname = view.findViewById(R.id.button_user_nickname);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">Bitmap</span> <span class="variable">bitmap</span> <span class="operator">=</span> BitmapFactory.decodeResource(getResources(), R.drawable.cr7);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">Bitmap</span> <span class="variable">circleBitmap</span> <span class="operator">=</span> Bitmap.createBitmap(bitmap.getWidth(), bitmap.getHeight(), Bitmap.Config.ARGB_8888);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">BitmapShader</span> <span class="variable">shader</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">BitmapShader</span>(bitmap, Shader.TileMode.CLAMP, Shader.TileMode.CLAMP);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">Paint</span> <span class="variable">paint</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Paint</span>();</span><br><span class="line">paint.setShader(shader);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">Canvas</span> <span class="variable">c</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Canvas</span>(circleBitmap);</span><br><span class="line">c.drawCircle(bitmap.getWidth() / <span class="number">2f</span>, bitmap.getHeight() / <span class="number">2f</span>, bitmap.getWidth() / <span class="number">2f</span>, paint);</span><br><span class="line">userProfileImage.setImageBitmap(circleBitmap);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>圆形头像框</p><p>circular_border.xml</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">shape</span> <span class="attr">xmlns:android</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:shape</span>=<span class="string">&quot;oval&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">stroke</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">        <span class="attr">android:width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;4dp&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">        <span class="attr">android:color</span>=<span class="string">&quot;@color/border_color&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">shape</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
